		<div class="article-details">
			<h4>
				<a href="https://www.driving.co.uk/news/interview/duke-of-richmond-75-years-goodwood-interview/">
					
					Duke of Richmond Q&amp;A: 75 years of Goodwood				</a>
			</h4>

			<hr class="red" />

			
			<div class="article-desc">
				We sit down with His Grace ahead of the 2023 Festival of Speed to discuss 75 years of Goodwood motorsport.			</div>

			<div class="article-date">
				Published 10 July 2023			</div>
		</div>
